      <title>特朗普的司法部叫停法学院学生无薪暑期实习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-s-doj-halts-unpaid-summer-internships-for-law-students</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据多位知情人士透露，美国司法部已撤回了志愿法律实习计划的邀请，并告知法学院学生将不再拥有暑期职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-s-doj-halts-unpaid-summer-internships-for-law-students</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 23:02:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
